								<th>관심 여행테마(최대 3가지)</th>
								<td><input type="checkbox" name="themaCode" value="1" onclick="javascript:chk(this)">자연
									&nbsp;&nbsp; <input type="checkbox" name="themaCode" value="2" onclick="javascript:chk(this)">문화관광
